data.title: Tacoma Dome Station
data.meta_description: Station maps, real-time arrivals, parking, bike and other amenity information for Tacoma Dome Station.
data.text:
Extra service on N Line and S Line from 10:00 AM through 6:00 PM on Sun Aug 25 due to special event

In effect: Aug. 25, 10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.

Routes: N Line & S Line

The Issaquah Transit Center Garage will experience a partial closure until further notice due to project work.

In effect: July 25, 9:01 a.m.

The Federal Way Transit Center Garage is experiencing a closure of the top level until further notice due to construction. All other levels of the garage will remain open during this time.

In effect: Sep. 12, 9:07 p.m.

Routes: 574, 577, 578 & 586
